            "content": "<section class=\"theme-agency-hero\">\n  <h1>We build digital products that ship</h1>\n  <p class=\"theme-agency-lead\">Strategy, design, and engineering under one roof — without the WordPress plugin treadmill.</p>\n  <p><a class=\"theme-agency-cta\" href=\"/team\">Meet the team</a></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"theme-agency-section\">\n  <h2>Services</h2>\n  <div class=\"theme-agency-grid\">\n    <article><h3>Product design</h3><p>Research, UX, and UI systems that scale across marketing and product.</p></article>\n    <article><h3>Engineering</h3><p>PHP, front-end, and integrations with clear ownership and observability.</p></article>\n    <article><h3>Content platforms</h3><p>Structured CMS models, blueprints, and migrations you can repeat.</p></article>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"theme-agency-section theme-agency-section--muted\">\n  <h2>Selected work</h2>\n  <p>Replace this block with case studies or embed entries from a portfolio type — the homepage is just HTML in <code>cms_pages</code>.</p>\n</section>",
